overview.en: Mgx is a de-centralized mining project. It is an original and new DAG structural algorithm-schema partition fusion algorithm (B-DAG algorithm). Through SDK, we can realize the seamless docking of entertainment social products with the function of snatching red envelopes on the chain.
overview.zh: Mgx是一个去中心化的可挖矿项目，原创全新DAG结构性算法-图式分区融合算法（B-DAG算法）。通过SDK可实现链上抢红包功能无缝对接娱乐类社交产品。
